      <acqinfo id="aspace_bb6d0de42ac786038b7c2d914b64e958">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The collection was purchased from Simmons &amp; Waters, secondhand book and print dealers in England, in 1959.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
